definition:
Someone descended from Zerah who was a man of the tribe of Simeon living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness, first mentioned at Gen.46.10; 
 son of: Simeon (H8095); 
 brother of: Jemuel (H3223), Jamin (H3226), Ohad (H0161), Jachin (H3199) and Shaul (H7586H); also called Zerah at Num.26.13,20; 2x27.11,13; 
Group of ze.rach (זֶ֫רַח "Zerah" H2226L) 
 § Zarhites , of Zerah
 descendants of Zerah
